message.body: Outstanding commencement speech!! Your going to need a manager to handle your speaking engagements...I'm available :-) I have a school for you to consider next
Thank you! I'm not sure if i have anything new to talk about lol...i threw everything but the kitchen sink in the last one! But I'm up for the challenge!
Nothing "New" is necessary, that speech will be relevant for a long time :-) !
Haha! Great! Please tell them as someone that's cares about their future i am glad for the assignment, but as their big cousin I'm sorry for giving them homework during summer break!
Lol...they will thank you in the future!
